            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="25452792">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/25452792/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p25452792-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 所以我觉得社会主义乃至马克思主义可以看成辉格的继承人</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-29 10:22</span>
                  
