                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p25452792-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>所以我觉得社会主义乃至马克思主义可以看成辉格的继承人
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
